unk_28bc3c5.value:
function Start(idActorKiller, idActorKilled)

-- Drop lore book.
	Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idActorKilled, s_lorebook)

end

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

-- Playing VFX for the prisoner's soul being released.
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectSize(idActorGizmo, 2.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroup(idActorGizmo, vfxBurst)
	Hydra.ActorSetPowerEffectDuration(idActorGizmo, 2.5)
	Hydra.ActorPlayEffectGroupActorToActor(idActorGizmo, idMarker, vfxLine)

-- Stake becomes vulnerable again.
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idStake, false)

end

unk_993f312.value:
T_MONSTERS = Hydra.ActorsLinkedByActorInGroup(idSelf, "MONSTERS")

-- Initial Setup
for i, idMonster in ipairs(T_MONSTERS) do
	--Munchin on snax
	SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE = Hydra.ReferenceAIState("GenericJobState");
	Hydra.ActorMergeAIState(Hydra.QuestGetOwner(), SNO_JOB_STATE_AI_STATE, idMonster, 0.0);
end

-- Set the stake invulnerable until the switch has been triggered.
	Hydra.ActorSetInvulnerable(idStake, true)
